{"tid":762361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度8男輪姦懷孕山羊，稱「愉快的晚上」","createTime":"2018-07-31T08:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T10:51:51.000Z","uid":147312,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"52bb812d8f4b7024703516cdf120b16d6baea0a3","tid":762361,"uid":147312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:09:36.000Z","msg":"印度8惡男飲醉酒輪姦懷孕山羊致死　事後向羊主炫耀：愉快的晚上<br />\n<br />\n印度哈里亞納邦的一條村莊近日爆出駭人聽聞的人獸交兇案！ 8名有多次案底的男子涉飲醉後，輪姦一頭7歲山羊。據了解，被害山羊已懷孕50周，被姦後不能行走及拒絕進食，於翌日傷重死去。<br />\n<br />\n羊主指其中一名作案惡男事後更向他嘲諷，指他們與山羊度過了一個愉快的晚上。印度警方日前表示已落案起訴涉事男子，即將展開拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/216930/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A68%E6%83%A1%E7%94%B7%E9%A3%B2%E9%86%89%E9%85%92%E8%BC%AA%E5%A7%A6%E6%87%B7%E5%AD%95%E5%B1%B1%E7%BE%8A%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%BB-%E4%BA%8B%E5%BE%8C%E5%90%91%E7%BE%8A%E4%B8%BB%E7%82%AB%E8%80%80-%E6%84%89%E5%BF%AB%E7%9A%84%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%8A?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F216930%2F%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A68%25E6%2583%25A1%25E7%2594%25B7%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E9%2586%2589%25E9%2585%2592%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E5%25A7%25A6%25E6%2587%25B7%25E5%25AD%2595%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25BE%258A%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%25AD%25BB-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2590%2591%25E7%25BE%258A%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%2582%25AB%25E8%2580%2580-%25E6%2584%2589%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2599%259A%25E4%25B8%258A%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=y8GnNjpPWm%2BETVwSsq17p7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=28f13f9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/216930/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A68%E6%83%A1%E7%94%B7%E9%A3%B2%E9%86%89%E9%85%92%E8%BC%AA%E5%A7%A6%E6%87%B7%E5%AD%95%E5%B1%B1%E7%BE%8A%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%BB-%E4%BA%8B%E5%BE%8C%E5%90%91%E7%BE%8A%E4%B8%BB%E7%82%AB%E8%80%80-%E6%84%89%E5%BF%AB%E7%9A%84%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%8A?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a><br />\n<br />\n印度男人係咪痴撚線連山羊都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0125616267b5442e3d6ebdee5d7611fc7fef8a6e","tid":762361,"uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:11:10.000Z","msg":"點解當年爆嬰兒潮果期鄰國同日本要捉d人去絕育<br />\n就係防止呢d無腦撚繼續繁殖"},{"pid":"e3c32be6c0d165e74774cea31f88aafc7b5b7ac1","tid":762361,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愉快的晚上"},{"pid":"52aa5afcf759bc56eca8b07e0ead08f145a767bb","tid":762361,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:13:28.000Z","msg":"山羊 = G"},{"pid":"a74b0c2c44c7f005d654cd87566b9b1931acfe91","tid":762361,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:15:53.000Z","msg":"又諗番起屌羊果個笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0a99d8b969f81190f2bde15c28cfc78db8c5e9","tid":762361,"uid":61177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a74b0c2c44c7f005d654cd87566b9b1931acfe91","tid":762361,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:15:53.000Z","msg":"又諗番起屌羊果個笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:16:32.000Z","msg":"搵羊個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a64ef71b09fba2d4f73dcc43de679b50ddda70c","tid":762361,"uid":21917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a74b0c2c44c7f005d654cd87566b9b1931acfe91","tid":762361,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:15:53.000Z","msg":"又諗番起屌羊果個笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:17:26.000Z","msg":"原來係真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b38480bf93674432b5d662555d6f4a4225a66c","tid":762361,"uid":68884,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fa0a99d8b969f81190f2bde15c28cfc78db8c5e9","tid":762361,"uid":61177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a74b0c2c44c7f005d654cd87566b9b1931acfe91","tid":762361,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:15:53.000Z","msg":"又諗番起屌羊果個笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:16:32.000Z","msg":"搵羊個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:18:05.000Z","msg":"那一晚，我走失了......"},{"pid":"fb079cee8900347403c36ae1d1e4541b05eb5510","tid":762361,"uid":49697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:18:37.000Z","msg":"睇黎同屌完騾仔返唔到轉頭係同一個道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873a474b0db59cf99cde6c145d8822ad3acbf03c","tid":762361,"uid":173397,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4786289a0cbcc6f6ae679b3ed5ccd28240df7909","tid":762361,"uid":61177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"873a474b0db59cf99cde6c145d8822ad3acbf03c","tid":762361,"uid":173397,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:21:08.000Z","msg":"係屌隻大肚既羊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e899449dd72e568bcd78bf5ba403c20babf4ea0d","tid":762361,"uid":12086,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"在一個古老的山鄉，發現了一個古老的村落。由於他們世世代代和外界隔絕，宛如桃源中人，外界對他們產生了濃厚的興趣。於是一個漂亮的女記者前往這落後的山鄉，去採訪當地人。<br />\n<br />\n她採訪的對象是一個六十多歲的老者，知道他們世世代代與世隔絕的生活以後，女記者驚訝，繼而是好奇，於是她打算描寫一下他們與世隔絕生活中的喜怒哀樂。<br />\n<br />\n「請問，多年來，您最高興的一件事情是甚麽？」，好奇的女記者問。<br />\n<br />\n「有一年冬天，隔壁老三家的羊走失了。」老頭說。<br />\n<br />\n「羊走失了，有甚麽值得高興的嗎？」女記者更好奇了。<br />\n<br />\n「羊丟了以後，我們幾十個人打着火把上山去找，找了三天三夜，終於在後山的一個角落裏面找到了」，老者吸了口煙，眯縫着眼睛回味無窮的說。<br />\n<br />\n「找到後怎麽了？」女記者好奇的問。<br />\n<br />\n「找到的時候天已經很晚了，我門在雪堆裏面紮了帳篷休息。外面的風很大。我們感到很無聊。於是大家就輪流上那只羊。好爽！」<br />\n<br />\n女記者顯然感到有點尷尬，她想避開這個話題。於是她打斷老者的話，問有沒有其他高興的事情？<br />\n<br />\n「有一年冬天，前邊老馬家的新媳婦在山裏面走失了。」老者說。<br />\n<br />\n「找到了嗎？」女記者追問。<br />\n<br />\n「我們幾十個人找了三天三夜，終於在後山的角落裏找到了。於是我們按下帳篷休息。冬天的晚上的風很大。我們大家都很無聊。於是我們就輪流上老馬他家的新媳婦，別提多爽了。」老者說着敲了敲手中的旱煙袋。<br />\n<br />\n女記者感到更尷尬了。她決定避開這個話題。於是她問到，在這幾十年與世隔絕的生活中究竟有沒有甚麽值得悲傷的事情？<br />\n<br />\n老者的臉色突變，手也開始顫抖，幾乎抓不住手中的旱煙。深陷的眼眶中滾出了兩滴渾濁的淚。嘴唇哆嗦了好幾下，他的身體也似乎在顫抖。沈默良久，他說：「一年冬天，我走失了......」"},{"pid":"2ebf5668567de7d3485fcbf210ad08ef8e41fcf1","tid":762361,"uid":151664,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T09:01:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">送咩咩妹去印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"aa5be3c363b21330cb004efc106facb10ca41577","tid":762361,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T10:51:51.000Z","msg":"好可憐嘅山羊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}